{"tid":1516601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831 set左死線 大家討論下後續活動","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T22:00:39.000Z","uid":237568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"abebcfca4699a78dea8907f00bb0bb60f448864a","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SCzHsn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSCzHsn9.jpg&h=bf381a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以預見西環上環金鍾一定重防<br />\n而且呈現包圍之勢<br />\n我地可以遊行<br />\n但係西環升級既話<br />\n非常不智<br />\n如果轉場有無提議<br />\n定好似8月5咁<br />\n7區狗屋？<br />\n大家討論下"},{"pid":"9a53d9c51e871f51234d8c9102cab26b5827a81b","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd88d6bbaadbf37be2cd04846a141d9d50e90838","tid":1516601,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f5d30e43bc5e37ce950ccb0fded90ce73923e60","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f47cae2851cbc824e76009cb754c2696795112bb","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f621f3998ae71a8982d3c15b44909aec9d9f763c","tid":1516601,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"831遊行<br />\n831<span style=\"color: red;\">死線</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPUwkJi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPUwkJi.png&h=5cdf89a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三罷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jzL9Ck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jzL9Ck.jpg&h=15ca9a42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2LO7o0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2LO7o0.jpg&h=5b0b7f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXXeivG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXXeivG.jpg&h=ae775cdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94fbf2bee9fde6650deea7f9d33a1667eafd055c","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"9a7465341471eb1b5d394d851c73c07f04e7ae29","tid":1516601,"uid":19743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n借個位黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人撐香港隊<br />\n入場向世界表達訴求<br />\n賽前有奏鄰國國歌儀式，大家識做!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eC7JUxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeC7JUxG.png&h=4352d932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3BKDZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3BKDZn.png&h=fd2e6806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQHFcjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQHFcjE.jpg&h=6cb0627d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHDpEVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHDpEVO.jpg&h=cd36f349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地仲可以用香港隊名義踢國際賽係因為我地同中國足協係完全分開運作<br />\n有自己既地方聯賽<br />\n如果可以既話<br />\n希望咁多位可以多多支持香港超級足球聯賽<br />\n因為香港足總成日話港超無出路<br />\n要返中國聯賽/大灣區聯賽"},{"pid":"b9ed37130af6de296dd4a99496d997fe2e147d64","tid":1516601,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d53a7f122269a814217e3551245b40e728356349","tid":1516601,"uid":231818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"d01440885a52b26d8486a1cb9509a2c18813d7ca","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"遊行一定會行<br />\n但預弟愚見<br />\n係西環警方plan好既地點開戰一定損失慘重"},{"pid":"b2da8f2545f3a7fd64c1fc2903c298c392d1dda0","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d01440885a52b26d8486a1cb9509a2c18813d7ca","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"遊行一定會行<br />\n但預弟愚見<br />\n係西環警方plan好既地點開戰一定損失慘重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76352dc3421f2a504ba601439f4257342deb3382","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f16d1629459b3777cfb93abf920e08cee1a1b22e","tid":1516601,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"full gear ready"},{"pid":"8d524462c6282018f6b9e8127c7f31c7088ea002","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16d1629459b3777cfb93abf920e08cee1a1b22e","tid":1516601,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"full gear ready"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"呢樣一定<br />\n但要圍咩<br />\n係邊打<br />\n要討論"},{"pid":"34aebe98cf30b19591c40d9920e2e5cabedb27de","tid":1516601,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"705a62a9cea8bbf5ecf0628bd5d8e3e2cb49a962","tid":1516601,"uid":237